<article class="item no-date" data-permalink="http://www.bibliocasselman.ca/en/about-us/library-news/202-2016-td-summer-reading-club">

	
	
	<div class="content clearfix">
		<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; text-decoration: underline;"><strong><img src="/images/photo/biblio15%20.jpeg.JPG" alt="biblio15 .jpeg" /></strong></span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style="color: #00ccff; font-size: 14pt; text-decoration: underline;"><strong>2016 TD Summer Reading Club</strong></span></span></span></p>
<p><img src="/images/bookflowers4.jpg" alt="bookflowers4" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/images/TD14.jpg" alt="TD14" width="202" height="157" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">August 1st to 24th, 2016<br /></span></strong></span></em></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The TD Summer Reading Club, a free program developed by Canadian Public libraries, is a great way to keep your kids engaged with reading.<br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Whichever method of reading you prefer, the Club is accessible to all!<br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Challenge yourself this summer!&nbsp; How many books can you read during school break?&nbsp; Whatever your challenge, register with the Club!<br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img src="/images/TD44.jpg" alt="TD44" width="182" height="112" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">2016 TD Club Activities</span></strong></span></em><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">&nbsp; </span></strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 10pt;"><span style="color: rgb(255, 0, 0);"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;">(Please note that activities are offered in french only)</span></strong></span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"></span></span><em><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"><br /></span></strong></span></em><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;"></span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The Library will be accepting registrations to the TD Club activities starting July 26th, 2016.&nbsp; <br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Whether you're on your own or with your friends, <strong>every Wednesday morning at 10:00 A.M. more specifically on August 3rd, 10th, 17th and 24th,</strong> all children between the ages of 6 and 12 as well as their parents are welcome at the Casselman Public Library for activities such as crafting and book reading.&nbsp; Our friendly staff will be waiting for you! <br /></span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">Please contact the Library for any information and/or registration to the TD Club and its activities, at 613-764-5505. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/images/TD34.jpg" alt="TD34" width="67" height="63" />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <br /></span></p>	</div>

	
	
		
</article>
</div><div class="grid-box width100">
<article class="item no-date" data-permalink="http://www.bibliocasselman.ca/en/about-us/library-news/200-mega-used-books-sale-2016-edition">

	
	
	<div class="content clearfix">
		<p><img src="/images/photo/biblio15%20.jpeg.JPG" alt="biblio15 .jpeg" />&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="color: #00ccff;"><span style="font-size: 18.6667px;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Mega Used Books Sale 2016 Edition</span></strong></span></span></p>
<p><span style="color: #00ccff;"><span style="font-size: 18.6667px;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></span></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/images/photo/Vente_livres.jpg" alt="Vente livres" width="366" height="100" style="border: 0px; cursor: default; vertical-align: baseline; outline: black solid 1px; color: #434343; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif; font-size: 61.3333px; line-height: 20px;" /></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">J.R. Brisson Complex</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">June 2, 3, 4, 2016</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">&nbsp;Opening Hours</span></span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Thursday, June 2nd: 10:00 A.M.-7:00 P.M.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Friday, June 3rd: 10:00 A.M.-7:00 P.M.</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-size: 14pt;"><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">Saturday, June 4th: 10:00 A.M.-5:00 P.M.</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">The Casselman Public Library will be holding its 5<sup>th</sup> annual used books sale at the J.R. Brisson Complex during the first weekend of June 2016.&nbsp; All are welcome to visit this sale and take advantage of the multitude of reading treasures for all ages.&nbsp; Profits will go towards the purchase of new books for the Library.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">You are also welcome to bring your used books at the Library. &nbsp;A return box is available for your convenience on the outside of the building (764 Br&eacute;beuf Street), or you may drop them during opening hours:&nbsp; Monday, Tuesday, Thursday from 2:00 P.M. to 8&nbsp;:00 P.M., Wednesday from 9&nbsp;:00 A.M. to 5&nbsp;:00 P.M., Friday from 2&nbsp;:00 P.M. to 5:00 P.M., Saturday from 9:00 A.M. to 12:00 P.M. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 14pt; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;">For more information concerning the used books sale or for any questions about the Casselman Public Library, please contact the Director Ms. Rachel Boucher at 613-764-5505or by e-mail at: <a href="mailto:rboucher@casselman.ca">rboucher@casselman.ca</a><a href="mailto:rboucher@casselman.ca.">.</a></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><img src="/images/photo/biblio15%20.jpeg.JPG" alt="biblio15 .jpeg" />&nbsp; &nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline; font-size: 14pt; color: #00ccff;"><strong>We Are Hiring</strong></span></p>
<p>Casselman Public Library is looking for a part-time (9 to 12 hours/week) reception clerk.</p>
<p>Your resum&eacute; should be forwarded by email to the attention of Ms. Rachel Boucher at : <a href="mailto:rboucher@casselman.ca">rboucher@casselman.ca</a>&nbsp;at the latest by 5:00 P.M., May 20th, 2016.</p>
<p>Please note that only those chosen for an interview will be contacted.</p>	</div>

	
	
		
</article>

<article class="item no-date" data-permalink="http://www.bibliocasselman.ca/en/about-us/library-news/190-td-club-mamiesa">

	
	
	<div class="content clearfix">
		<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; text-decoration: underline;"><strong><img src="/images/photo/biblio15%20.jpeg.JPG" alt="biblio15 .jpeg" /></strong></span><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color: #00ccff; font-size: 14pt; text-decoration: underline;"><strong>2015 TD Summer Reading Club - The ''Mamies'' are inviting you!<br /></strong></span></span></span></p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/images/file.png" alt="file.png" /> As part of its 2015 TD Summer Reading Club, the Casselman Public Library is happy to announce that Mamie Mado and Mamie Sue will offer a story telling hour every Wednesday morning at the Library!</p>
<p>Mamie Mado will be offering story telling hours in French from 10:00 to 11:00 A.M. on July 8th, 15th, 22nd, 29th and August 5th, 2015 at the Library.</p>
<p>Mamie Sue will be offering story telling hours in English from 11:00 to 12:00 P.M. on July 8th, 15th, 22nd, 29th and August 5th, 2015 at the Library.</p>
<p>Children from 6 to 12 and their parents are most welcome; children under 6 must be accompanied by an adult.</p>
<p>As space is limited, please register beforehand at the Library. We are looking forward to sharing some precious story telling moments with all! See you soon!</p>	</div>

	
	
		
</article>
